description: Hello. The studio has a very comfortable queen size bed, small couch, coffee table, wi fi, kitchen. 2 bathrooms are shared with two other studios. Very comfortable. 1 block to subway station.
name: Studio in Manhattan 7 blocks north of Central Park
review:
It's good cost-effective apartment in NYC. Certainly, the bathroom is not wide. However, the room is big enough to long stay and stylish.
We saved money to stay and visited many sights in NYC.
